Requirements :-

Make a lib which will help to print Labels of names for Invitation
Records will be provide.
Lib should able to print Labels in required format and it also should able to filter the records

Label should be in format of :-

+----------------------+
| Mr John Smith        |
|----------------------|
| New Delhi, Karnataka |
| India                |
+----------------------+

          OR

+----------------------+
| Mr Smith, John       |
|----------------------|
| New Delhi, Karnataka |
| India                |
+----------------------+

They are very particular about the size of the boders with a margin of one space between the text and the borders. 

filtering options
> "by country"
> "by age and country"
> "by age"

Input :-
> options from command line (need to process input);
> records file (need to reed file);


